                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">DRAGON BUSTER CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
